resources.string: CUREYA (registered as Aspexx Health solutions Pvt. Ltd., under MCA) is DPIIT recognized startup, registered under \'STARTUP INDIA SCHEME\'. CUREYA primarily objective is \'Health for All\', by reducing the medical expenditure, eliminating the information asymmetry, promoting health awareness and achieving inclusive & holistic approach for healthcare treatments.
Made with love in india to empower healthcare services.
